## Prerequisites

### Helm

```bash
curl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/helm/helm/main/scripts/get-helm-3 | bash

helm repo add gitlab https://charts.gitlab.io/
helm repo update
```

### Required Images in Internal Registry

Pull on an internet-connected machine, SCP to registry server, then push:

```bash
# On internet-connected machine
podman pull docker.io/gitlab/gitlab-runner:latest
podman pull registry.gitlab.com/gitlab-org/gitlab-runner/gitlab-runner-helper:x86_64-v18.10.1
podman pull docker.io/alpine:3.21
podman pull docker.io/ubuntu:22.04

podman save -o /var/lib/longhorn/gitlab-runner.tar docker.io/gitlab/gitlab-runner:latest
podman save -o /var/lib/longhorn/gitlab-runner-helper.tar registry.gitlab.com/gitlab-org/gitlab-runner/gitlab-runner-helper:x86_64-v18.10.1
podman save -o /var/lib/longhorn/alpine.tar docker.io/alpine:3.21
podman save -o /var/lib/longhorn/ubuntu.tar docker.io/ubuntu:22.04

tar -czf /var/lib/longhorn/runner-images.tar.gz \
  /var/lib/longhorn/gitlab-runner.tar \
  /var/lib/longhorn/gitlab-runner-helper.tar \
  /var/lib/longhorn/alpine.tar \
  /var/lib/longhorn/ubuntu.tar

# SCP to registry server
scp /var/lib/longhorn/runner-images.tar.gz root@img-registry.apps.ttmtech.com:/root/
```

On the registry server:

```bash
cd /root
tar -xzf runner-images.tar.gz

podman load -i /var/lib/longhorn/gitlab-runner.tar
podman load -i /var/lib/longhorn/gitlab-runner-helper.tar
podman load -i /var/lib/longhorn/alpine.tar
podman load -i /var/lib/longhorn/ubuntu.tar

REGISTRY="img-registry.ttmtech.local:5000"

podman tag docker.io/gitlab/gitlab-runner:latest $REGISTRY/gitlab/gitlab-runner:latest
podman tag registry.gitlab.com/gitlab-org/gitlab-runner/gitlab-runner-helper:x86_64-v18.10.1 $REGISTRY/gitlab/gitlab-runner-helper:x86_64-v18.10.1
podman tag docker.io/alpine:3.21 $REGISTRY/gitlab/alpine:3.21
podman tag docker.io/ubuntu:22.04 $REGISTRY/gitlab/ubuntu:22.04

podman push $REGISTRY/gitlab/gitlab-runner:latest --tls-verify=false
podman push $REGISTRY/gitlab/gitlab-runner-helper:x86_64-v18.10.1 --tls-verify=false
podman push $REGISTRY/gitlab/alpine:3.21 --tls-verify=false
podman push $REGISTRY/gitlab/ubuntu:22.04 --tls-verify=false
```

