## Using the Runner

### Tagging Jobs (Recommended)

To explicitly route jobs to the Hillsborough runner add the `hil-k8s` tag:

```yaml
build:
  stage: build
  tags:
    - hil-k8s
  image: img-registry.ttmtech.local:5000/gitlab/ubuntu:22.04
  script:
    - make build
```

> **Note:** Without tags any untagged job on `gitlab.ttmtech.com` can land on this runner. Using the `hil-k8s` tag ensures explicit routing.

### Increasing Concurrent Jobs

To increase from 4 to 8 concurrent jobs update the values file and upgrade:

```yaml
concurrent: 8
```

```bash
helm upgrade --install gitlab-runner gitlab/gitlab-runner \
  -n gitlab-runner \
  -f ~/gitlab-runner-values.yaml
```

